    <li>Guideline utilization resource unit handbook. Edmonton (Alberta): CancerControl Alberta; 2013 Jan. 5 p. </li>
</ul>
<p>In addition, a final approval checklist for photodynamic therapy is available in Appendix B in the <a href="/web/20180713052022/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=48137&amp;contentType=summary&amp;redirect=http%3a%2f%2fwww.albertahealthservices.ca%2fassets%2finfo%2fhp%2fcancer%2fif-hp-cancer-guide-gi011-barretts-esophagus.pdf" title="Alberta Health Services Web site">original guideline document</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180713052022im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/>.</p></div></p>
